During the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], the '''Barefoot Band''', who, as their name implied, always performed in their bare [[Limb/Legends|feet]], were a popular [[Band/Legends|band]] who frequently performed in the [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]] of [[Bestine (city)/Legends|Bestine]], the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

